               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="167v">1v-167v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="apodous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s38IHA">قران, First half (ǧuz’ 1-15)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>سورة الفاتحة مكية وهي سبع ءايات بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم الحمد لله رب العلمين الرحمن الرحيم ملك يوم الدين</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#167v">-167v</locus>الله او ادعوا الرحمن اياما تدعوا [فله الاسماء الحسنى] ولا تجهر بصلوتك ولا تخافت بها <note>The ends of the lines are not visible due to tight binding.</note>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The text ends with the verse 17:110, i.e. the end of part 15 is missing. Fols 163-167 damaged in the lower corner close to the binding. Corrections in the margins in red. Connector wa appears alone in the end of the line. Some lines end with undotted letters/words that are then repeated with dots in the beginning of the next line. Vocalized.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
